      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks but the antacids didnt really do anything and the pain is still super sharp. i really dont want to go to the er tonight if i can help it, it's so expensive and i have work early tomorrow. do you think it's safe if i just take a high dose of the ibuprofen to numb it out so i can sleep? i feel like if it was actually serious it wouldnt just be a stomach ache.",
